    "body": "请基于以下业务需求设计 RESTful 接口契约：\n业务场景：{{business}}\n技术栈：{{framework}}\n\n请输出：1) 接口列表（method/path/请求体/响应体）2) 主要数据模型（含校验规则）3) 错误码规范。"
  },
  {
    "id": "backend-crud",
    "roleId": "backend",
    "name": "生成 CRUD",
    "description": "为指定实体生成 Controller/Service/Repository",
    "category": "生成",
    "parameters": [
      {
        "name": "entity",
        "label": "实体名",
        "hint": "如：User",
        "required": true
      },
      {
        "name": "fields",
        "label": "字段列表",
        "hint": "如：id:Long, name:String, email:String",
        "required": true,
        "multiline": true
      }
    ],
    "body": "为实体 {{entity}} 生成完整 CRUD：字段：{{fields}}\n要求：Controller/Service/Repository/DTO；含参数校验；分页查询；统一响应包装。"
  },
  {
